Just copy paste the following program in Emacs and the Makefile given after that:
        //Note:This listing will not compile. It has errors.
#include <stdio.h

int main()
{
  return 0
}

To compile and execute a program create a new file, edit it and save it. The extension
        of file should be *.c. For example, myprogram.c. After
        that you can give this command at terminal. Here is the corrected code for
        you.#include <stdio.h>

int main()
{
  return 0;
}
